properties.name: Best Small Town
properties.description: Posted by VeniviciI believe this is the town of Dell. It consists of one small gas station and several eighteen-wheelers that stop for the night on their way through Wendover. Total estimated population at any given time: <7.

properties.name: Best Thanksgiving
properties.description: Posted by VeniviciI was having Thanksgiving at George\'s sons house when I became horribly sick. The closest hospital from Wendover is Cottonwood in MURRAY! Those were the longest 2 hours of my life. That\'s when I had pneumonia, the flu and gastroenteritis all in the same week.

properties.name: Best Use of Product Placement
properties.description: Posted by VeniviciThere is a Cola vending machine in this open-pit mine. You can see it if you stand at the visitor center by the big tire and look straight across the pit. I seriously doubt it works because of its remote location and lack of electricity. But it is cool anyways.
